text: Victoria Țurcanu (née Gurdiş; born 22 February 1996) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a defender for the Moldova women's national team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Sportspeople from Bălți Category:Moldova women's international footballers Category:Women's futsal players
